        <mxCell id="XmzAUjS4AAH027HiIq-t-404" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;UML Arrow Legend&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;A ─────────▷ B&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Generalization / Inheritance&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Solid line with a hollow triangle.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;The triangle points to the superclass.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Example: HeaderPanel extends JPanel.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;A - - - -▷ B&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Realization / Interface Implementation&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Dashed line with a hollow triangle.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;The triangle points to the interface.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Example: FileChatHistoryDAO implements ChatHistoryDAO.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;A ◆──────── B&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Composition&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Solid line with a filled diamond.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;The filled diamond is placed at the owning class.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Example: MainFrame owns HeaderPanel.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;A ────────&amp;gt; B&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Association&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Solid line with a normal arrow.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Class A has a field/reference to class B.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Example: TranslationPanel has a reference to HistoryPanel.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;A - - - -&amp;gt; B&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Dependency / Uses&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Dashed line with a normal arrow.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Class A temporarily uses class B, for example as a method parameter, return type, or local variable.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Example: TranslationService uses TranslationRequest.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="614" width="688" x="-1180" y="-230" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
